summary:
Experienced Android developer with knowledge of: Architectures, Development Design Patterns, Dependency Injection, Android SDKs, Kotlin, Java.
I think like a user of the app that I develop. That always help to improve UX and UI in project. Refactoring is another important part of development which can help with having always stable app for users. That's why I always learn more on different courses/tutorials about modern technologies, methodologies, new features of Kotlin or new Android version.

I enjoy traveling, playing guitar, skating on my longboard or biking.

Please feel free to reach out to me via LinkedIn Messenger or via email if you're interested in working together or would like to get to know me more!
